Class PropertiesKeyValueStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • xdi2.core.impl.keyvalue.AbstractKeyValueStore

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyValueStore

    public class PropertiesKeyValueStore
extends AbstractKeyValueStore
implements KeyValueStore
    This class defines access to a properties file. It is used by the PropertiesKeyValueGraphFactory class to create graphs stored in properties files.
